               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter. The front matter contains the prayer of Adam based on the Hebrew letters. The word for God is rubricated. The midpoint of the psalms is unmarked.The spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters in Psalm 118 are the recent, simple ones. Contains the long version of Psalm 151. Canticle four is Prayer of Hana, Mother of Samuel the prophet. The Song of Songs is the common version.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
